{"tid":712373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美駐華使館微博 竟有大批中國網民留言撐美國 更希望美國滅共產黨不要手軟","createTime":"2018-06-22T04:58:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T04:42:56.000Z","uid":54373,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"a4080b9619d1124adb9fa223a7e7d924a6443947","tid":712373,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:58:31.000Z","msg":"美國駐華大使館周二在微博上載總統特朗普就中美貿易爭端發表的聲明，吸引逾三千個留言及讚好、五千多次轉發。<br />\n<br />\n留言中除了我們一貫常見指罵美國的言論外，意外地竟有大批網民以簡體字支持美國加徵關稅。我們留意到有部分言論發表不久就被刪除，亦有網民表示留言被刪帖，有人就表明是來看留言的。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">以下是部分留言節錄：<br />\n<br />\n「求求你們再來(加關稅)4000億吧」<br />\n<br />\n「再猛烈些吧，世界民主需要你」<br />\n<br />\n「中國人民幸福就靠特朗普了」<br />\n<br />\n「斬草要除根，別留餘地」<br />\n<br />\n「想起了鴉片戰爭觀看中英交戰的民眾，每當有中國官船被擊沉，民眾就歡呼」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/35654405_1753238801487265_7704762529741799424_n.jpg?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=048286a7034c333f2256528e18eb4e33&amp;oe=5BB0B8A3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F35654405_1753238801487265_7704762529741799424_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3D048286a7034c333f2256528e18eb4e33%26oe%3D5BB0B8A3&h=9ccc8d89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/35694766_1753238808153931_4776800856391548928_n.jpg?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=3a9db25bcc1578de35ab675e55a3805a&amp;oe=5BA9166E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F35694766_1753238808153931_4776800856391548928_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3D3a9db25bcc1578de35ab675e55a3805a%26oe%3D5BA9166E&h=8e14b187&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/35653252_1753238821487263_1148643588331012096_n.jpg?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=7559389b59023cb1505eb64024fe85ad&amp;oe=5BE872C2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F35653252_1753238821487263_11486